行一大段路去gate</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下, 如果我係九龍站CHECKIN完, 寄埋行李, 到左機場個陣, <br />\n係可以直去T1 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，直穿過關去gate<br />\n但市區check in寄倉早截過機場櫃位"},{"pid":"4f1ed49c667e38053485f74dc50a760c3c3f7b20","tid":472320,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"有活動偷多半個鐘輕鬆坐地鐵入東涌轉巴士都夠時間啦"},{"pid":"e63c0a94bb84ccfae5f6b33c40071aedddc2827b","tid":472320,"uid":63722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"機鐵香港站chk in再，到機場T2過安檢(因為人少)，搭無人駕駛到T1過對面就另一架無人駕駛到中場，如果架機唔係泊中場係5xx位上就搭一次無人駕駛上一層就到5xx位。<br />\n建議你唔好T1過安檢，2200呢段時間大把歐洲機客係T1 chk in，過安檢時間太難預。<br />\n利申機場仔冇老點你"},{"pid":"e6ba1e86af687c875546f09873be01cdc399a3ff","tid":472320,"uid":63722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反正UO都Delay<br />\n驚咩</blockquote><br />\n準時過國泰同港龍，廉航唔一定遲，國泰太多西客大搖大擺遲上機，老逢全機等佢"},{"pid":"94330f205fde039bb32e9d150514affa3fc6bf95","tid":472320,"uid":1968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要咁遲出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實個晚有個好重要活動，我諗9點9左右先係北角碼頭走。<br />\n如果唔去個活動，準時6點鐘收工就去得機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n取捨一下</blockquote><br />\nON9明知自己無時間仲要勉強自己去活動</blockquote><br />\n佢好似連地鐵機鐵都唔識搭咁<br />\n又有重要活動<br />\n係偽政府高層官員都唔定<br />\n<br />\n遲到冇乜所謂啦<br />\n飛機點敢唔等佢<br />\n<br />\n成機人以至航空公司都表示冇問題啦</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府高官就唔洗搭uo 又趕頭趕命<br 